item.description: Al-Araby Al-Jadeed Corona Egypt: Doubts about the efficiency of the return-to-work plans The Egyptian government continues to rush towards a full return to service and financial activities after the end of the month of Ramadan, despite the worsening situation of the new Corona epidemic, the steady increase in the number of daily casualtiesâ€¦ and the failure of the state to conduct random tests even in areas that witnessed high infection rates.
